                                </path>
                            </g>
                        </svg>

                        <span class="flex-grow"></span>

                        To build strong, caring relationships with our clients
                        and remove the fear and myths of dealing with the IRS.
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center bg-brand-blue p-4 rounded"
                    >
